  "keyFeatures": [
    "Simple Tool, Resource, and Prompt definitions with Standard Schema support",
    "OAuth 2.1 authentication with pre-configured providers (Google, GitHub, Azure)",
    "Multiple transport types: stdio, HTTP streaming, SSE, and edge runtime support",
    "Session management with session ID and request ID tracking",
    "Custom HTTP routes for REST APIs, webhooks, and admin interfaces",
    "Edge runtime support for Cloudflare Workers and Deno Deploy",
    "Stateless mode for serverless deployments",
    "Built-in OAuth proxy with Dynamic Client Registration (DCR) and PKCE",
    "Progress notifications and streaming output",
    "Image and audio content support",
    "Embedded resources for simplified tool responses",
    "CLI tools for testing (fastmcp dev) and debugging (fastmcp inspect)",
    "HTTPS support with SSL certificate configuration",
    "Configurable ping behavior and health-check endpoints",
    "Typed server events and error handling"
  ],
